headline: Barclays Initiates Coverage On ON Semiconductor with Equal-Weight Rating, Announces Price Target of $75
summary: Barclays  analyst Tom O'Malley   initiates coverage on ON Semiconductor (NASDAQ:ON) with a Equal-Weight rating and announces Price Target of $75.
